1. add to portainer via git repository https://github.com/lewis198804-byte/plate_planner.git

2. compose path : docker-compose.yaml

3. Create .env file in container root and add open_ai_key


*BACKUPS

1. docker compose holds variable for default backup directory if none set in portainer environment (/tmp/backups)

2. if enabling backups, create the folder you want to store them in, then pass the path to this folder to the container via portainer environment variable (BACKUP_DIR). Defaults to /app/backups